  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Scum is a sci-fi action-roguelike survivors game with dialogs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive wave after wave of enemies until you face the final boss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create different builds during each run by selecting different level-up rewards from a wide range of weapons and equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather minerals in each run and bring them to your base of operations to buy new weapons and upgrades and help yourself in the next run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player weapons aim and fire automatically.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-= Rogue Scum Features =-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Huge hordes of enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Awesome weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlimited upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Base of operations on a spaceship Big Fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Lots of fun tasks to finish (achievements)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cool characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play as Operator - an independent agent operating on the fringes of known space, looking to make profit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10+ hours of gameplay to unlock everything (depending on player skill and luck).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3660900/extras/0c50a71deba249d215adf40ec116b69f.avif?t=1749320840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3660900/extras_big/0c50a71deba249d215adf40ec116b69f.avif?t=1749320840 width=800 height=154 /></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Scum is a sci-fi action-roguelike survivors game with dialogs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive wave after wave of enemies until you face the final boss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create different builds during each run by selecting different level-up rewards from a wide range of weapons and equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather minerals in each run and bring them to your base of operations to buy new weapons and upgrades and help yourself in the next run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player weapons aim and fire automatically.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-= Rogue Scum Features =-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Huge hordes of enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Awesome weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlimited upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Base of operations on a spaceship Big Fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Lots of fun tasks to finish (achievements)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cool characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play as Operator - an independent agent operating on the fringes of known space, looking to make profit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10+ hours of gameplay to unlock everything (depending on player skill and luck).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3660900/extras/0c50a71deba249d215adf40ec116b69f.avif?t=1749320840\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3660900/extras_big/0c50a71deba249d215adf40ec116b69f.avif?t=1749320840 width=800 height=154 /></span></h2>",
